Statement: collection of expressions

    1) General Purpose Statements:
       - Declaring variables, methods, classes, etc.
       - Creating objects, accessing variables, methods, etc.

    2) Conditional Statements: executes block of instructions under perticular condition
       - if, if-else, switch-case

    3) Iterative Statements:
       - for, while, do-while

    4) Transfer statements:
       - break, continue, return

    5) Exception Handling statements:
       - try-catch-finally, throw, throws

    6) Synchronised statements:
       - synchronised method, synchronised blocks